~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : tell                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : tell <username> <message>

   This allows you to speak privately to another user without having to
   find a private room. 

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : shout, wake
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
